column5: Hi! Never fished in Huntsville/Haliburton area, what lake would you suggest for pike/bass maybe walleye this time of year?  Thanks!!!

Lots to chose from I find this tool handy  http://www.web2.mnr.gov.on.ca/fish_online/fishing/fishingExplorer_en.html  Enter the species and the distance from the city Huntville or Haliburton.  For digging stuff out I like to start at smaller lakes
